<h2 id="图片-pic-cpic"><a href="#图片-pic-cpic" class="headerlink" title="图片(pic|cpic)"></a>图片(pic|cpic)</h2><p>pic+ Tab → <img src="/link" alt="图片无法显示时的名"><br>cpic+ Tab → <div align=center>&lt;img src&#x3D;”link”width&#x3D;”100%” height&#x3D;”50%” &gt;</div></p>
